<h1>Our Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
3cixty provides this Privacy Policy to inform users of our policies and procedures regarding the collection, use and disclosure of personally identifiable information received from users of this platform, located at https://dev.3cixty.com.
</p>
<p>
By using the 3cixty platform, you are consenting to our processing of your information. Processing means using cookies on a computer or touching your information in any way.
</p>

